Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.95,0:22:33.81,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}我知道你自始至終
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.85,0:22:38.99,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}都在心裡喊「謝謝」
